> INBIO It performs fingerprint matching on the control panel. The FR transfers the LINBIO fingerprint templates via RS-485 to quickly and accurately match the templates stored in the database . The INBIO control panel is easily installed on the network and supports both TCP / IP and Rs-485a. An automatic detection tool that allows you to modify changes directly and easily on the network.

Firmware upgrade of the INBIO control panel can be done on-site or project. Store up to 3,000 fingerprints, 30,000 card users, and up to 100,000 transactions and transactions. A real-time controller is supported on-board SD card. Data is saved in case of power loss. INBIO continues to work if the network connection is interrupted. Along with relay contacts for controlling door locks, the added easy-to-program modifications can be used for additional monitoring and interface of lights, alarms, announcers, intrusion detection panels, or additional locking devices or gate controllers.

The INBIO control panel comes in three sizes to suit the needs of the project and reduce the cost of unused energy. Single door, 2 doors 4 doors models can be combined together in the system structure. Forgery detection system. First-card entry, multi-card entry , password coercion, and I / O modification links to the firmware console

The SDK is freely available for DEVELOPMENTOEM for integrating INBIO controllers with security, personnel management or existing applications. Upon request, ZK can also provide customized INBIO firmware to meet any customer requirements.
